data.description: Renovated Mid-Century rambler in the heart of WELSH, LA!  If you've been looking for the perfect updated mid-century style home, look no further than 411 E. NICHOLS! Situated on 2 lots, this home is definitely one to see. Traditional mid-century styling greets you as you pull up to this lovely home proudly boasting a fully fenced yard, covered 2 car carport, rear covered patio, shed and large shop! Inside you will notice newly updated modern design elements have been added throughout. A formal living room off the front entry displays built in bookcases, a large brick ensconced fireplace and mantle, and freshly painted on trend color schemes with hard surface floors throughout. A master bedroom ensuite sits to the right with board and batten wall features and creative touches thoughtfully added to enhance this homes obvious beauty. To the rear of the home sits a lovely large formal dining/kitchen combo with a pass thru fireplace, new lighting design, gorgeous thick marble countertops draped over brand new cabinets and new built-in appliances.  A spacious fully enclosed sun porch exits to the rear of the dining space and connects to an ample laundry with a full sink and tons of additional storage. 2 more bedrooms and a full bath round out this homes abundant offerings. With all of this packed under one roof, this one is guaranteed not to last long! Call or schedule your showing today!
